# Unity Multiplayer API SDK Test Cases
# Compatible with Unity JsonUtility

## Test Configuration
- Base URL: https://api.michitai.com/unity
- Test API Token: YOUR_API_TOKEN
- Test Player Token: PLAYER_TOKEN

## Player Management Tests

### Register Player Test
```bash
curl -X POST "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_players.php/register?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"player_name":"TestPlayer","player_data_json":"{\"level\":1,\"score\":0}"}'
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "player_id": "123",
    "private_key": "abc123...",
    "player_name": "TestPlayer",
    "game_id": 1
}
```

### Login Player Test
```bash
curl -X PUT "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_players.php/login?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&game_player_token=PLAYER_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "player": {
        "id": 123,
        "game_id": 1,
        "player_name": "TestPlayer",
        "player_data_json": "{\"level\":5,\"score\":100}",
        "is_active": 1,
        "last_login": "2023-01-01 12:00:00",
        "last_heartbeat": "2023-01-01 12:00:00",
        "last_logout": null,
        "created_at": "2023-01-01 10:00:00",
        "updated_at": "2023-01-01 12:00:00"
    }
}
```

### Player Heartbeat Test
```bash
curl -X POST "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_players.php/heartbeat?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&game_player_token=PLAYER_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Heartbeat updated",
    "last_heartbeat": "2023-01-01 12:00:00"
}
```

### Logout Player Test
```bash
curl -X POST "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_players.php/logout?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&game_player_token=PLAYER_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Player logged out successfully",
    "last_logout": "2023-01-01 12:00:00"
}
```

### List Players Test
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_players.php/list?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&api_private_token=YOUR_PRIVATE_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "count": 5,
    "players": [
        {
            "id": 123,
            "player_name": "TestPlayer",
            "is_active": 1,
            "last_login": "2023-01-01 12:00:00",
            "last_logout": null,
            "last_heartbeat": "2023-01-01 12:00:00",
            "created_at": "2023-01-01 10:00:00"
        }
    ]
}
```

## Game Data Management Tests

### Get Game Data Test
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_data.php/game/get?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "type": "game",
    "game_id": 1,
    "data_json": "{\"difficulty\":\"normal\",\"max_players\":10}"
}
```

### Get Player Data Test
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_data.php/player/get?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&game_player_token=PLAYER_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "type": "player",
    "player_id": 123,
    "player_name": "TestPlayer",
    "data_json": "{\"level\":5,\"score\":100,\"inventory\":[\"sword\",\"potion\"]}"
}
```

### Update Game Data Test
```bash
curl -X PUT "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_data.php/game/update?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&api_private_token=YOUR_PRIVATE_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"difficulty":"hard","max_players":12,"last_updated":"2023-01-01T12:00:00Z"}'
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "Game data updated successfully",
    "updated_at": "2023-01-01 12:00:00"
}
```

### Update Player Data Test
```bash
curl -X PUT "https://api.michitai.com/unity/game_data.php/player/update?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&game_player_token=PLAYER_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"level":6,"score":150,"last_played":"2023-01-01T12:00:00Z"}'
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
