    "success": true,
    "message": "Player data updated successfully",
    "updated_at": "2023-01-01 12:00:00"
}
```

## Time Management Tests

### Get Server Time Test
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.michitai.com/unity/time.php?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "utc": "2023-01-01T12:00:00+00:00",
    "timestamp": 1672574400,
    "readable": "2023-01-01 12:00:00 UTC"
}
```

### Get Server Time with Offset Test
```bash
curl -X GET "https://api.michitai.com/unity/time.php?api_token=YOUR_API_TOKEN&utc=1" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```

**Expected Response**:
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "utc": "2023-01-01T13:00:00+01:00",
    "timestamp": 1672578000,
    "readable": "2023-01-01 13:00:00 UTC",
    "offset": {
        "offset_hours": 1,
        "offset_string": "+1",
        "original_utc": "2023-01-01T12:00:00+00:00",
        "original_timestamp": 1672574400
    }
}
```

